3a0a			; | ACTIVE ( -- s ) Push the next char for an activity indicator to TOS | DONE 
3a0a			;  
3a0a			; | | To display a pulsing activity indicator in a processing loop do this... 
3a0a			; | | e.g. $ff $00 do active . ..... Your code ..... loop 
